title: Which Men’s Tennis Player Will Be No. 1 at the End of the Year?
description: Novak Djokovic has taken the top spot for the last two years, but, with his struggles, now it’s up for grabs.
dc:creator: Cindy Shmerler
media:description: Novak Djokovic has won 17 of his last 18 matches, but he is ranked No. 7, his lowest ATP ranking since August 2018 because he has played just 10 events all season.
